name: Self-portrait 14
description: #NFTsForAll #WorldArtDay The project is about the problems with accept their body.  I don’t know what to do. It’s grown a moustache. I don’t know what to do. Eyelid lift. What is eyelid surgery? I don’t know what to do. How to treat the pimples?  The project is about contemporary social beauty stereotypes and the influence on the individuals.  Whenever I look at my photos or videos of me, I'm so sad of myself. The project is about mother and daughter.
